{"tid":1891728,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有水塘水庫，不會死。重建海水化淡廠。大馬水平260倍，船運","createTime":"2020-02-22T05:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:31:23.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffccee0f6b3efac511c8b2c54997d7de92ae571","tid":1891728,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zeno.lung/posts/2664301953805916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzeno.lung%2Fposts%2F2664301953805916&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=39add7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/zeno.lung/posts/2664301953805916</a><br />\n<br />\n留言中，有人講水。香港有水塘水庫，不會死。可重建海水化淡廠，以前香港海水化淡是世界第一。留言中，有人說新加坡貴，那是與大馬比較，但中國的東江水比大馬水貴260倍。未重建好之前，還可以用油輪運水購買。<br />\n<br />\n留言中有人講電，香港的電本來就自給自足。中國自己常停電，電力又不足，說香港買中國電根本離譜。留言中有人講減排，這無異是，根據國際標準，香港學童活動空間不足，九成九幻稚園要殺校，十分on9。而且透過更新技術，煤炭發電一樣能比現在環保，一樣能減排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2017/06/30/new-thermal-power-generation-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2Fnew-thermal-power-generation-tech%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=bd9324ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2017/06/30/new-thermal-power-generation-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n留言中有人說疏果八、九成來自中國。錯，水果主要產地是美國，其他產地還有泰國、菲律賓等。疏菜在1985年，香港本地生產30%，現在香港還是有產疏菜，但這個政府的寫明政策是「不與主要來源地競爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos/status/1226021958040424448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos%2Fstatus%2F1226021958040424448&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=098b3003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos%2Fstatus%2F1226021958040424448&h=d5cec166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos/status/1226021958040424448</a><br />\n<br />\n... 這些圖是數年前的數據，下列文章有更新,總體依然大同小異:<br />\n-米飯:泰國(52.9%)、越南(29.3%)、中國(7.7%)<br />\n- 牛肉:巴西(50%)、美國(21%)、中國(2.3%)<br />\n-豬肉:巴西(27%)、中國(13%)／豬排：中國(22%)、美國(17%)<br />\n-雞肉:巴西+美國(70%)、中國(19%)<br />\n<a href=\"http://thenewslens.com/article/30973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F30973&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=88a35267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://thenewslens.com/article/30973</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/supplement/20191029/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsupplement%2F20191029%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=cb148e0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsupplement%2F20191029%2F&h=b60ed8e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/supplement/20191029/</a>"},{"pid":"0d957b2c748dfba0a8503ac633b25826de1f4787","tid":1891728,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec1bd8ee72043f2258a6fc8b3a633f56667e6ca","tid":1891728,"uid":326402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7ec8a703d9114c789fbabb4eb436a1fb4330d73","tid":1891728,"uid":79442,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"屌左咁多年海水過濾廠都未起 真on9"},{"pid":"94d180852ffcd26ad24e65fab6e152b6beecb7af","tid":1891728,"uid":126856,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:27:12.000Z","msg":"反而想知香港人接唔接受到再生水呢個概念。再生水即係NEWater，新加坡現時近半既水資源供應都係從再生水度來，但係再生水係用家居廢水經過生物化學處理，再做Reverse Osmosis 過濾出乾淨食水。"},{"pid":"5b5166063027ae483de2feaa9d12e5bf7869ddf1","tid":1891728,"uid":2584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"符合衞生標準就得"},{"pid":"ef5b134c646087cdc6e32527311ecb47e9a4153e","tid":1891728,"uid":314509,"like":0,"